System:

    melt of 100 chains of 8 atoms, with angle and dihedral potentials.

    Requires a version of mcSim compiled with angles (option -a) 
    and dihedrals (-d) enabled.

Usage
----- 

Change directory (cd) to an example subdirectory, then enter:

MC simulation:

    mcSim -e -p param.nve -c commands

Restart and extend previous simulation

    mdcim -e -r restart -c commands.rst
